query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	webhookGetSubscriptions (query: $query)

		id
		rowId
		name
		service
		endpoint
		externalId
		events
		secret
		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

		endpoint
		externalId

		secret
		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

	}
}
